Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:04.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Fem un pas decidit cap a un futur gloriós. Estem del tot mentalitzats!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:06.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,En Heiji i en Shinichi, els detectius adolescents,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:09.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,s'enfrontaran en un combat de deduccions en una estació d'esquí!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Qui resoldrà el misteri? Sempre descobreix l'única veritat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:15.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sembla un nen, però té el cervell d'un adult i és el detectiu Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:19.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,Seaside moon, seaside sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.96,0:00:23.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,itsumademo kawanaru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:30.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,kokoro wo mou ichido kimi ni todoketai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:33.28,Songs,,0,0,0,,Glorious mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:39.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,So give me the reason why
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:43.88,Songs,,0,0,0,,leave me here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:46.52,Songs,,0,0,0,,The reason why
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:50.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,I don't know how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:53.96,Songs,,0,0,0,,So must be the truth, baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:00:58.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,shall we end then it's up to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:02.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is a diferent day, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:05.44,Songs,,0,0,0,,And I know when I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.28,0:01:10.08,Songs,,0,0,0,,Glorious mind, glorious sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:14.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,Omoikiri naitara.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.24,0:01:21.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kinou made no koto ha zenbu wasureyou!
